ZH: 公司授权您代表我们参加会议。
EN: The company authorized you to represent us at the meeting.

ZH: 这封信是授权您进入特定的建筑物。
EN: This letter authorizes you to enter a specific building.

ZH: 我们需要授权合同才能与该公司合作。
EN: We need an authorized contract in order to work with that company.

ZH: 所有员工必须接受授权培训。
EN: All employees must undergo authorized training.

ZH: 我们将授权您查看这份文件。
EN: We will authorize you to view this document.

ZH: 他授权了她管理他的财产。
EN: He authorized her to manage his property.

ZH: 这是一项全权授权，你需要同意条件。
EN: This is a full authorization, you need to agree to the terms.

ZH: 只有经过授权的人员才能进入这个区域。
EN: Only authorized personnel are allowed to enter this area.

ZH: 授权书必须由公司高层签署。
EN: The authorization letter must be signed by senior company executives.

ZH: 我们将对软件进行授权来保护知识产权。
EN: We will authorize the software to protect intellectual property.

ZH: 授权代表将与政府官员讨论决策。
EN: The authorized representative will discuss decisions with government officials.

ZH: 请提供证据以证明您的授权。
EN: Please provide evidence to prove your authorization.

ZH: 我们希望您能授予我们交易的授权。
EN: We hope that you will grant us authorization for the transaction.

ZH: 授权书经过法律部门的审查后才能生效。
EN: The authorization letter will only take effect after being reviewed by the legal department.

ZH: 公司授权您为公司代言品牌。
EN: The company authorizes you to endorse the brand on behalf of the company.

ZH: 你可以授权亲人作为你的医疗代理人。
EN: You can authorize a family member to be your medical proxy.

ZH: 授权书将保护您的权益。
EN: The authorization letter will protect your rights.

ZH: 我需要得到你的授权才能进行下一步。
EN: I need to get your authorization before proceeding to the next step.

ZH: 被授权的人必须严格遵守机密协议。
EN: The authorized person must strictly abide by the confidentiality agreement.

ZH: 我们需要向该机构申请授权。
EN: We need to apply for authorization from the institution.
